Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.73,0:00:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,（運動流汗系愛愛4鏡頭）\N（體育運動系 八卦海）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,（網球）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,（劍道）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,（游泳）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,0:01:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,（排球）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.77,0:01:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,（運動流汗系愛愛4鏡頭）\N（體育運動系八卦海）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:02:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,庭球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,96 97 98 99
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,100
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是八卦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,教練
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就你一個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我在練習準備比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.19,0:02:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真是努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要充滿自信比賽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我還不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要想太多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,教練難得過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你把把關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是舉手之勞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-開始吧-謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,再揮揮着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,把屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,對著教練
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你練習過度了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,還有就是想得太多反而慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,想太多也不是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,教練來給你扶一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這也是訓練的一環
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這個肌肉的部分有點奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,教練
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續你的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要注意你的協調
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這個部分的肌肉發力\N有點問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,表情有點奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是身體比較僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:06:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣放鬆很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你很懂事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,身體倒是很纖細啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,睜眼看著教練
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡的肌肉我幫你看看情況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要教練幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,得告訴你肌肉的發力方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼發車這樣的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不要想下流的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,上半身基本上没問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那接下來是下半身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,跪爬在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好好的看著這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡怎麼濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:11:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,越來越濕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,知道為什麼濕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那得尋找原因才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不看看裡面不知道原因啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,得好好確認一下才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不看看正面不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,現在在做色色的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好好的抱住自己的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,身體的緊張是不是得到了釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,來看看我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,現在怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,變大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很僵硬對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,給我按摩一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,給我舔舔 讓它舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好好的舔舔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這個很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,跟誰比的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好好的舔舔這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,只用嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:19:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,舔著你也舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:22:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.83,0:22:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,放鬆了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,放鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我還有一個特別按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那就躺下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是特別按摩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.78,0:23:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,對教練的特別按摩滿意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.54,0:24:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.65,0:24:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.28,0:24:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.15,0:24:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.66,0:25:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,自己在動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.27,0:25:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.77,0:25:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,因為舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.51,0:25:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.35,0:25:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.55,0:25:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,看著教練 說肉棒舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.06,0:25:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.26,0:25:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-誰的肉棒\N-教練的肉棒舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.46,0:26:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,流了好多水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.08,0:26:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,都這樣了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.32,0:26:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就這麼想要教練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.62,0:26:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,想要
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.72,0:27:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.93,0:27:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,深處舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.21,0:28:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,教練的特訓怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.85,0:28:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-舒服嗎-舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.01,0:28:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,到深處了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.39,0:29:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.79,0:29:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.47,0:29:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,特訓還沒有結束哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.63,0:30:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,深處舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.03,0:30:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.51,0:31:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,教練也好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.78,0:31:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,身體裡的濃郁物質要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.75,0:31:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,射出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.22,0:31:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,射哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.13,0:31:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.03,0:31:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,射裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.10,0:31:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.80,0:31:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.83,0:31:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.49,0:32:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.26,0:32:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,上面還有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.04,0:33:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,(弓道）
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.19,0:33:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧 海海
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.37,0:33:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣不管會出炎症啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.18,0:33:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.72,0:34:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這招最有用 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.97,0:38:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.11,0:39:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.15,0:39:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.40,0:39:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,轉身
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.20,0:40:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翹起來
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.34,0:40:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.40,0:41:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,已經濕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.85,0:42:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,自己拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.90,0:42:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,掀起來讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.86,0:43:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,已經好濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.16,0:43:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-舒服嗎-舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.11,0:44:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好好的掀起來
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.22,0:44:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好好讓我玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.82,0:44:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,給我舔舔
