Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.34,0:51:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.31,0:51:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.80,0:51:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.24,0:52:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎麼樣-舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.39,0:53:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,要插了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.00,0:53:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.29,0:53:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.75,0:54:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.82,0:55:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.50,0:55:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,背對著我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.21,0:55:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.58,0:55:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,翹起來對
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.83,0:55:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-這裡舒服嗎-舒服
